summary: The document is a declassified communication pertaining to the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992. It details identities and contact information of individuals with potential links to Cuba, referencing a Madrid telephone directory under a specific name. The document notes the absence of a file for further details, suggesting possible redaction or information unavailability.
key_findings: References the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992.
Identifies individuals with Cuban citizenship at birth.
Mentions a Madrid telephone directory with listings under a specific name.
Indicates no file is available for further details, hinting at possible redaction or lack of information.
